{"tid":1432350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係FB瘋傳既一芳香港總部員工-你問我答","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:50:23.000Z","uid":293897,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cdaf895e354a99526b64d17e8ead41ae02470235","tid":1432350,"uid":293897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲,<br />\n我借左戰友AC開一個你問我答,大家有咩想問可以隨便問 (利申:關於到所有合約問題我答唔到,因為我地自己已經內部做緊野)..以下係我證明<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7633G4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7633G4.png&h=7eefb688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後我老闆就有野同大家講...如果你有野問佢就入去下面條link輪姦佢啦 PLS (佢應該解答到大家點解要用私人身份..因為我地仲有好多法律問題跟進緊)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thomaslauhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthomaslauhk%2F&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO71znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=c32b1399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/thomaslauhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今鋪係一芳打緊扙，香港人都打緊仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今鋪要風雨同路.....<br />\n香港人救香港人....<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n#藍絲唔洗再forward我個post啦，良心既野你地識條撚咩"},{"pid":"f3dc7634c8c89734459dcdb49861585541ed0049","tid":1432350,"uid":142854,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"你d綠茶點解可以落糖咁難飲"},{"pid":"3b2639f00c147959c34401796978b8a7c96e4d93","tid":1432350,"uid":133354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"1. 聽講有好多分店都係特許經營，咁你個老闆有咩做？<br />\n<br />\n2. 叮噹之後有咩公仔換？<br />\n<br />\n3. 點解無烏龍茶賣？"},{"pid":"8f7dc7efd37ffb8abab2cac93e4f686adaffd3fe","tid":1432350,"uid":293897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3dc7634c8c89734459dcdb49861585541ed0049","tid":1432350,"uid":142854,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"你d綠茶點解可以落糖